# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.


## [1.0.1] - Unreleased

### Changed

- Increased font-size of non-<pre>-wrapped <code>.
- Added "Page X of Y" centered between pagination buttons

## [1.0.0] - 2019-05-04

### Added

- Started project - 2019-05-01
- added LICENSE content
- fleshed out layout
- widgets:

    - Hero Avatar
    - Author Bio
    - Navigation
    - External Links
    - Recent Posts
    - Tag Cloud

- organized stylesheet

- build manifest
    - .builds/publish.yml

